{"type":"message","id":"78df836d","parentId":"407e20a3","timestamp":"2026-03-28T08:12:06.190Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, I got the search results. Let me analyze what I found:\n\n1. There are multiple songs titled \"无岸\" (No Shore)\n2. One version by 小蓝背心 (Xiao Lan Beixin) released on September 6, 2024, by 讯飞音乐 (iFlytek Music)\n3. There's mention of an AI version sung by 曾一鸣 (Zeng Yiming) in a 2026 forum post, but details are unclear\n4. Another mention of an AI song on Bilibili with singer labeled as \"唐三藏\" (Tang Sanzang)\n5. Several other non-AI versions by different artists\n\nThe search results are somewhat limited and don't provide comprehensive information about an AI-generated song specifically. Let me do another search with more specific terms to find AI-generated versions of \"无岸\".","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b9c465dffa24422a94b34352","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"无岸 AI生成 人工智能歌曲\"","timeout":60}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":29139,"output":231,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29370,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774685520641}}
